                </h2>

                <div class="alert alert-info">
                    <i class="bi bi-info-circle me-2"></i>Manage your account security settings
                </div>

                <div class="mb-4">
                    <h5 class="fw-bold mb-3">Recent Activity</h5>
                    <div class="d-flex border-start border-3 border-success ps-3 mb-3">
                        <i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success me-3"></i>
                        <div>
                            <div>Logged in from San Francisco, CA</div>
                            <div class="small text-muted">Today, 09:24 AM</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="d-flex border-start border-3 border-primary ps-3 mb-3">
